{"tid":1577491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新屋嶺 對面就係 沙嶺公墓","createTime":"2019-09-17T17:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T16:30:03.000Z","uid":227801,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"385eb83e74a345a60b63ce7a0f21ebd6027cdcdf","tid":1577491,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sKUyTnu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsKUyTnu.jpg&h=78adaed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/16931/%E7%94%9F%E6%AD%BB%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2-%E6%B2%99%E5%B6%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%A2%93%E5%A2%B3%E9%81%8A-%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%A4%E9%AD%82%E5%8C%96%E4%BD%9C%E7%84%A1%E6%83%85%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC%E5%90%88%E8%91%AC%E9%BB%83%E5%9C%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F16931%2F%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2-%25E6%25B2%2599%25E5%25B6%25BA%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25A2%2593%25E5%25A2%25B3%25E9%2581%258A-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25AD%25A4%25E9%25AD%2582%25E5%258C%2596%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2583%2585%25E8%2599%259F%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E5%2590%2588%25E8%2591%25AC%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%259C%259F&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5ClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=f3d7a306\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/16931/%E7%94%9F%E6%AD%BB%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2-%E6%B2%99%E5%B6%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%A2%93%E5%A2%B3%E9%81%8A-%E7%84%A1%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%A4%E9%AD%82%E5%8C%96%E4%BD%9C%E7%84%A1%E6%83%85%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC%E5%90%88%E8%91%AC%E9%BB%83%E5%9C%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n【生死教育】沙嶺公墓墳遊　無名孤魂化作無情號碼合葬黃土<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n突發<br />\n<br />\n撰文：呂凝敏<br />\n<br />\n2016-04-18 21:18<br />\n<br />\n最後更新日期：2018-06-14 17:36<br />\n<br />\nT2009 151&hellip;&hellip;T2014 240&hellip;&hellip;一個個曾經真實地活着、有名有姓的人，撒手人寰後，因遺體無人認領，只能化作一串如同囚犯編號的數字，墓碑上沒有照片、也沒有性別、再沒有名字，更重要的是，沒有親人、摯友陪他們走過最後一段路。數不盡的無主孤魂長埋沙嶺黃土。<br />\n七年過後，每年數以百計的遺體會被起骨、火化。這一刻，一眾無主孤魂，連僅有的號碼也會失去，所有骨灰會集中混葬在一個面積只得約兩呎乘兩呎、只得年份做單位的墓碑下，從此結伴長眠⋯⋯在沙嶺公墓中，連鮮花和香燭也是稀有品，陪伴他們的，只有婆娑樹影和一群渴望遇到血肉之軀的蚊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/80620/org/446d9eea94974189a91179d1a4a42ce7.jpg/gFgjF6zSUKNbW3gGJRfQfTW6eOklHuSOywj3iMsI94g?v=w1120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F80620%2Forg%2F446d9eea94974189a91179d1a4a42ce7.jpg%2FgFgjF6zSUKNbW3gGJRfQfTW6eOklHuSOywj3iMsI94g%3Fv%3Dw1120&h=82c8b318&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f677bcec842bf9cb0cd11841ebfb8930b88710a","tid":1577491,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c490ed9aa5a59e319f2d477d421b3cad3b4ffc34","tid":1577491,"uid":84102,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:26:46.000Z","msg":"睇吓有無啲新翻嘅土<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72747bf60252852ae0dae45ddd990e7cc963e45","tid":1577491,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd8c4496db942ff993f7a55f9e84aa1bb32d3d2","tid":1577491,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e498d4b19157164ebc790a0fb3eaeac3997faa77","tid":1577491,"uid":3501,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T17:34:46.000Z","msg":"無人認領嘅應該會係要行到最入面<br />\n前面個啲全部跟鄉下<br />\n利申唔熟 每年去一次"},{"pid":"9e404ab1400eb